An kashe daruruwan mutane a Indonesia sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru.
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu yayin da wata babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami suka addabi tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, a cewar jami'ai a ranar Asabar, yayin da wasu da dama suka nutse a bakin tekun.
A ranar Juma'a ne, a bakin rairayin bakin teku na birnin Palu, daruruwan mutane sun taru don yin biki, sa'ad da igiyar ruwa mai tsawon mita shida (18 feet) ta afka bakin tekun da yamma, ta hallaka mutane da yawa da kuma lalata duk abin da ke cikin hanyar.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
"Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta zo jiya, mutane suna kan rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu ba, kuma sun zama wadanda abin ya shafa", in ji Sutupo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar rage radadin bala'i ta Indonesiya, BNPP, a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta.
"Tsunami bai zo da kansa ba, ya kwashe motoci, katako, gidaje, ya buge komai da ke ƙasa", in ji Nugraho, ya kuma ce tsunami ya yi tafiya a cikin teku a cikin saurin kilomita 800 a kowace awa (497 mph) kafin ya buge gabar tekun.
Ya ce wasu sun tsere ta hanyar hawa itatuwa don tserewa tsunami.
An ceto mutane 16,700 a cibiyoyin 24 na Palu.
Hotunan sama da hukumar ta bayar sun nuna cewa gine-gine da shaguna da dama sun lalace, wasu gadoji sun rushe kuma wasu masallatai sun nutse cikin ruwa.
A ranar Asabar, an ci gaba da girgizar kasa a garin da ke bakin teku.
An ji jerin girgizar kasa a yankin da ke da mutane miliyan 2.4.
A wata sanarwa da hukumar nazarin fasahar zamani ta kasar Indonesia (BPPT) ta fitar, ta ce karfin da girgizar kasa ta saki a ranar Juma'a ya ninka na bam din da aka jefa a Hiroshima a yakin duniya na biyu, wato, kusan sau 200.
Ya ce yanayin garin da ke ƙarshen wani dogon, kunkuntar bakin teku zai iya ƙara girman tsunami.
Nugraho ya bayyana lalacewar a matsayin "mai fa'ida" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, manyan kantuna da otal-otal sun rushe.
Ya ce wasu gawarwakin wadanda abin ya shafa sun makale a karkashin rubabbun gine-ginen da suka rushe, ya kuma ce mutane 540 sun ji rauni, sannan 29 sun bace.
A cewar Nguroho, ana iya samun asarar rayuka da lalacewa a yankin Donggala, wanda ke kan gabar teku, kusan kilomita 300 (190 mi) arewa da Palu, kusa da cibiyar girgizar.
Daga Donggala, "sadarwar ta lalace gaba daya ba tare da wani bayani ba", in ji Ngoroh.
