Lokacin da Trump ya yi gangamin West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi wani gangamin kamfen a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin jerin tarukan da aka shirya biyar a makon gobe, tare da wasu wurare kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan da aka zaɓe shi ya cika wani sabon matsayi a Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi niyyar samun goyon baya domin yana ganin 'yan Republican za su rasa iko a majalisar dokoki idan aka gudanar da zaben raba gardama a watan Nuwamba.
Wane lokaci ne za a yi a taron gangamin Trump na West Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
Lokaci na rally na Trump na West Virginia yana da karfe 7 na yamma ET a daren yau, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron West Virginia na Trump a kan layi ta hanyar YouTube Live Stream a ƙasa.
Ana sa ran cewa a wannan makon za a iya gabatar da ƙarar da aka yi wa mai gabatar da kara na Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, a wani taron gangamin Trump.
Amma babban abin da za a mayar da hankali a kai shi ne, a ci gaba da bai wa 'yan Republican damar yin zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A cikin mako mai zuwa, za a yi wasu tarurruka biyar don ƙarfafa masu ba da agaji da masu goyon baya don kare da kuma fadada rinjaye da 'yan Republican ke da shi a Majalisar Dattijai da Majalisar Dokoki.
A cewar wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa, Trump yana son shiga jihohi da dama, domin ya mallaki majalisa, kuma ya yi hakan ne don ya samu damar yin aiki a lokacin yakin neman zaben.
Rahoton ya ce, "yanayin da aka tsara a yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, na iya gayyatar masu goyon bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma samun rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
Wannan ita ce ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda a jihar West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben da aka kada a 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a.
A wani bangare kuma, Trump ya yi kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar Sanata Patrick Morris, dan Republican na West Virginia, wanda ya sha wahala a zaben.
Shimon Haider, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, ya ba da rahoton cewa, "ba zai yi kyau ba idan Trump ya zo don ya ba da goyon baya ga zaben", in ji Reuters.
