An sake jinkirta jigilar sabon jirgin yaƙi na Jamus
A shekarar 2014 ne ake sa ran a tura sabon rundunar jiragen ruwan na rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus domin maye gurbin jiragen ruwan yakin da aka yi amfani da su a lokacin yakin sanyi, amma ba za a iya yin hakan ba har sai shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ya yi kuskure da kuma tsadar da ake kashewa a kan jirgin ruwan.
A cewar jaridar Direct da ke magana da wani kakakin soji, an dage kaddamar da jirgin ruwan "Rhineland-Falz", wanda zai zama jigon sabon jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg-class, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya shigar da jirgin ruwan a cikin 2014, amma wasu batutuwa bayan isar da su sun lalata makomar wannan babban buri.
Jiragen ruwan Baden-Württemberg guda hudu da rundunar ta sake yin oda a 2007 za su maye gurbin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
An gano cewa suna dauke da manyan bindigogi, da kewayon makamai masu linzami da kuma makamai masu linzami, da kuma wasu fasahohi masu zaman kansu kamar radar, inverted da acoustic signatures.
Sauran manyan fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin aiki, watau, za a iya tura sabbin jiragen yaƙi daga manyan tashoshin jiragen ruwa na gida har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, Direct ya ce, saboda jinkirin jinkirin da ake yi na jiragen ruwa na zamani - wanda aka ce ya ba da damar Jamus ta tsara makamashi a kasashen waje - sun riga sun zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka shiga sabis.
Abin takaici, jirgin ruwan F125 ya ƙi zama jirgin ruwa na hukuma na rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus a bara, kuma ya yi sanarwa ta hanyar mayar da shi zuwa Blohm da Voss Shipyard a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta mayar da wani jirgin ruwa zuwa ga mai gina shi a bayan da aka kai shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da shi ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi nuni da cewa akwai wasu muhimman abubuwa game da shi, kamar "rashin kayan aiki da kayan aiki" wanda zai sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka tura shi cikin yaƙi.
Rashin software na iya zama wani ɓangare na babban tasiri, saboda kusan masu aikin jirgin ruwa 120 ne ke aiki da jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg - suna amfani da rabin ƙarfin mutum a kan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Hakanan, jirgin yana da nauyi wanda zai rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance damar da rundunar ta ke da ita ta ƙara sabbin abubuwan da za su sabunta a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa nauyin "Rhine-land-Folz" na 7,000 na dubu biyu ya ninka sau biyu na jiragen ruwa masu nauyi da Jamus suka yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
Ban da kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikata - ya zama matsala.
An ce ya kai €2.2 billion ($3.6 billion) daga €2.2 billion da aka fara.
Waɗannan matsalolin sun fi muhimmanci a lokacin da ake neman samun sabbin jiragen ruwa a Jamus, a lokacin da ake ta yin gargadin cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwan sun "ci gaba da ficewa daga jiragen ruwa masu karfin aiki".
Ofishin ya ce wannan matsalar ta kara yin tsami a tsawon lokaci, saboda an soke tsoffin jiragen ruwa amma ba a samar da wasu masu sauyawa ba.
Ya yi baƙin ciki cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg-class da zai iya sake shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
